I'm sorry, I fixed the last problem.  Now I have a problem when I try 
to import my heterogeneous interface.  My cti file reads:

stoichiometric_solid(name = 'Pt111',
                     elements = E O Pt',
                     species = 'all'
)


when I try to import this phase into MATLAB with the command:

>>pt = importPhase('Ptsurf.cti')
